Battle: Triple Battle
Navi: MegaMan.EXE only (no Link Navis)
Reveal setup: Off
Patch: bn6_bingus patch (only bn6_bingus and bn6_soundmod_bingus are acceptable, do not use any other patches)
ModCards: Disabled
Giga Chips from opposite versions are not allowed (i.e. HubBatch J in Gregar, ColForce Q in Falzar)

- If you are not present 15 minutes after bracket start you will be DQ'd. No shows after 10 minutes on each following round will also be DQ'd.
- The following EXE6 exclusive chips are not allowed: (if you use a save created by Tango, these chips will not be available)

Gregar X
Falzar X
DblBeast W
GunDelEX G
Django D
Django2 D
Django3 D
Count H
