rechlDRBZb5BsC4lQ,None,N/A,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/121220,rect1f7F7XIFKqj2u,"recIQPH4peWxZPpTV, rechlDRBZb5BsC4lQ",Double Elimination,2/3,2/3,"1) Tournament will use the ""Easy Password Romhack"" version (search ""redearthep"" on fightcade2). lobby's description has archive.org link, where you can download the romhack file
